Comment: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:02.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:11.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:27.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:32.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:47.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:52.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:02.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:06.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:21.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:21.74,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:24.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
